 commons-fileupload-1.3.1.jar； commons-io-2.4.jar； mysql-connector-java-5.1.39-bin.jar；   二、实现流程 1. 图片添加界面：add.jsp &lt;%@ page language=&quot;java&quot; contentType=&quot;text/html; charset=utf-8&quot;pageEncoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;%&gt;&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;&lt;jsp:useBean id=&quot;DBBean&quot; scope=&quot;page&quot; class=&quot;com.zeng.lab06.DBBean&quot;/&gt;&lt;%DBBean.getConnect();String createSQL = &quot;CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS lab06(id int PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,title varchar(255),author varchar(255),file varchar(255))&quot;;DBBean.createTable(createSQL);%&gt;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;&gt;&lt;title&gt;Insert title here&lt;/title&gt;&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;href=&quot;https://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot;&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;#upload {width: 30%;height: 400px;border-width: 1px;border-style: inset;margin-top: 8%;margin-left: 35%;background-color: white;margin-top: 8%;}#form{margin-top: 28%;margin-left: 10%;width: 80%;}&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;upload&quot;&gt;&lt;form id=&quot;form&quot; action=&quot;../UploadServlet&quot; method=&quot;post&quot; enctype=&quot;multipart/form-data&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;input-group mb-3&quot;&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;placeholder=&quot;title&quot; aria-label=&quot;title&quot;aria-describedby=&quot;basic-addon2&quot; name=&quot;title&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;input-group-append&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-text&quot; id=&quot;basic-addon2&quot;&gt;标题&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;input-group mb-3&quot;&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; class=&quot;form-control&quot;placeholder=&quot;name&quot; aria-label=&quot;name&quot;aria-describedby=&quot;basic-addon2&quot; name=&quot;author&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;input-group-append&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;input-group-te